dit gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p style="margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: inherit !important;"><font color="#000000">Sailor make some of the world's finest quality fountain pens. Founded in 1911 by Kyugoro Sakata, who was introduced to the fountain pen by a British sailor, their pens are beautifully-made and they regularly produce some truly remarkable limited editions.</font></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1675760922517" class="gf_row gf_row-gap-15" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1675760922517" data-layout-lg="3+3+3+3" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="3+3+3+3" data-layout-sm="6+6+6+6" data-layout-xs="12+12+12+12" style="display: block; flex-wrap: unset; visibility: visible;" data-row-gap="15px"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-3 gf_col-md-3 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1675760922437" data-id="1675760922437" style="display: block; flex-direction: unset; justify-content: unset; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675761431424" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1675761431424" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><a href="/search?q=tea%20time&uff_tzjcfd_vendor=Sailor" target=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/a15d2769-16d3-4a24-b7c0-9ab0667460d1/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/Tea-Time-Around-the-World-tile.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" width="750" height="1000" natural-width="750" natural-height="1000" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></a></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-3 gf_col-md-3 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1675760947056" data-id="1675760947056" style="display: block; flex-direction: unset; justify-content: unset; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1697116238297" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1697116238297"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Sailor's Professional Gear range is a collection of pens that represents the brand's century of experience in constructing top quality writing instruments. These are traditionally-styled, with a smooth cylindrical barrel and which involve the use of different materials.</p><p><br></p><p>In Morocco, mint tea is an important part of day to day life, prepared by steeping green tea and mint in a teapot and then sweetened with sugar and is regarded as a symbol of Moroccan hospitality. When served to guests, they're traditionally served in 'Kissan' glasses that feature some wonderfully exotic patterns.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-3 gf_col-md-3 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1675760947026" data-id="1675760947026" style="display: block; flex-direction: unset; justify-content: unset; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675762811332" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1675762811332" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><a href="/products/sailor-professional-gear-slim-fountain-pen-tea-time-around-the-world-moroccan-mint-tea-mint-sugar-14k-nib" target=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/aa098fed-890e-4f70-8dca-95f9bec8428e/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/Tea-Time-Around-the-World-tile-001.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" width="750" height="1000" natural-width="750" natural-height="1000" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></a></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-3 gf_col-md-3 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1675760947134" data-id="1675760947134" style="display: block; flex-direction: unset; justify-content: unset; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675761807904" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1675761807904" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><a href="/products/sailor-professional-gear-ballpoint-pen-tea-time-around-the-world-moroccan-mint-tea" target=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/01c6ad71-0222-4126-a7cc-13eda77a3148/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/Tea-Time-Around-the-World-tile-002.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" width="750" height="1000" natural-width="750" natural-height="1000" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></a></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1675767368661" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1675767368661" data-layout-lg="6+6" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="6+6" data-layout-sm="6+6" data-layout-xs="12+12" style="display: block; flex-wrap: unset; visibility: visible;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1675767368623" data-id="1675767368623" style="display: block; flex-direction: unset; justify-content: unset; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675767519795" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1675767519795" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-exc=""><a href="/products/sailor-professional-gear-regular-fountain-pen-veilio-acrylic-blue-green-21k-nib-extra-fine" target=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/20ccdcdd-a382-411a-b3f1-a167f38687d9/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/VEILIO-screen.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" width="1779" height="1000" natural-width="1779" natural-height="1000" style="" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></a></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675770662767" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1675770662767"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Professional Gear Veilio</h2></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675770760680" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1675770760680"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p>Peer into the internal components through the transparent marble-effect barrel, in its pure and lustrous beauty.&nbsp;Other barrels and caps are shaped and polished by grinding the surface, yet it is difficult to polish the inner surface without leaving cutting marks.&nbsp;Sailor made this possible by carefully grinding the inner surface. The result is a smooth finish, tailored to be attractive both inside and out.&nbsp;</p></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1675767384572" data-id="1675767384572" style="display: block; flex-direction: unset; justify-content: unset; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675767638977" class="element-wrap" data-icon